## Add static IP to eth1

Use the following commands to add a static IP to eth1:
```bash
ip addr add 20.1.1.2/24 dev eth0
ip link set eth0 up
```

Or this on `edit config` in the gns3 node

```Plaintext
auto eth0
iface eth1 inet static
	address 20.1.1.2
	netmask 255.255.255.0
	up ip link set eth0 up
```
